{"tid":1815641,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發 小英再多一條片有提及香港","createTime":"2020-01-07T16:05:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T04:28:05.000Z","uid":7628,"like":259,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"f7e662b96763a7fb52051156660f7f16e47bcc9f","tid":1815641,"uid":7628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T16:05:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jqtpKLSukwk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjqtpKLSukwk&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=f413ac00\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jqtpKLSukwk</a><br />\n除咗琴日條片之外，再多一條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2Uz8Z5Piubg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2Uz8Z5Piubg&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=c3fe26e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2Uz8Z5Piubg</a><br />\n<br />\n呱吉幾個月前已經有出過片支持香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dzbFKP7rhxM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdzbFKP7rhxM&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=63e6c552\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dzbFKP7rhxM</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以去條片度留言多謝小英同呱吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f318434c1de4d0a5788a67005dfd911ab39117d4","tid":1815641,"uid":7628,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T16:06:20.000Z","msg":"星期六的下午，你有什麼計畫？<br />\n<br />\n你可能會想去喝杯咖啡、吃個甜點、到河邊騎單車，用一個下午的滿足，讓你覺得未來24個小時的人生不是虛度。<br />\n<br />\n但就在幾百公里外，卻有另一群人帶著裝備、在煙塵中奔跑、在不確定的未來中，度過星期六。<br />\n<br />\n這個星期六，你也可以選擇去投票。<br />\n<br />\n你的選擇，將會影響未來4年的台灣，所以更應該要把票投給能夠為台灣作出正確選擇的人。<br />\n<br />\n最後幾天，我沒有對手那麼多的廣告資源，只有你們每一個人，請大家幫忙分享，讓更多人看到。<br />\n<br />\n1月11日，#一個拉一個， #為了台灣回家投票。"},{"pid":"687eebe4c401d2894f0847f82e5c8cab6a33ac85","tid":1815641,"uid":7628,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T16:06:45.000Z","msg":"► 加入小英Line好友：<br />\n<a href=\"https://page.line.me/iing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpage.line.me%2Fiing&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=7af2d049\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://page.line.me/iing</a><br />\n<br />\n► 蔡英文Instagram：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tsai_ingwen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftsai_ingwen%2F&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=d1ace42f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/tsai_ingwen/</a><br />\n<br />\n► 蔡英文Facebook：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tsaiingwen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftsaiingwen%2F&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=56596096\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tsaiingwen/</a><br />\n<br />\n► 蔡英文Twitter：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/iingwen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fiingwen&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=0912b73c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/iingwen</a>"},{"pid":"0411515d2bd5a2fa921b26aaeb5721e54bdd48cc","tid":1815641,"uid":7628,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T16:07:44.000Z","msg":"多一個朋友=少一個敵人"},{"pid":"32e68a093175cb302bebf022de720670e56563a4","tid":1815641,"uid":7628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T16:10:37.000Z","msg":"小英加油1/10"},{"pid":"99483ae9629b55ea9fe8a0d9501ac14198c2880d","tid":1815641,"uid":7628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T16:10:48.000Z","msg":"小英加油2/10"},{"pid":"bb15dc25fd363ba3529fa01b61bd4c88050bbd38","tid":1815641,"uid":7628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"ci